    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine has a persistent knock and the transmission slips between second and third gears, suggesting a major overhaul is necessary. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly 'as-is,' making it a potential project for a mechanic or a source for parts.",
