    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean and presents well, though it does have some minor rock chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with no major stains or tears, though there is some light creasing on the leather seating surfaces. All electronics and mechanical systems are in proper working order, and the car drives smoothly, making it a reliable and attractive option for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
