    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly such a gem. It\u2019s been well-loved and is still in really solid shape, running smooth and ready to hit the road with a new owner. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend trip, this car is super reliable and a total joy to drive. I've taken great care of it, and it shows! Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining precise toe and camber alignment. While the finish shows minor road rash and the interior bolsters exhibit typical light patina, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak performance. A true driver\u2019s car with a clean service history.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used sedan. Reliable performance. Clean interior. Regular maintenance performed. Minor surface wear only. Solid daily driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 330i in Mineral Grey Metallic. This vehicle strikes an excellent balance between sporty performance and executive comfort. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, with only minor stone chips consistent with light use. Inside, the Oyster Dakota leather upholstery is supple and clean, showing minimal wear on the driver's bolster and absolutely no tears or odors. All cabin technology, including the iDrive infotainment system, backup camera, and dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the 2.0L turbocharged engine runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service record at authorized centers. The car handles beautifully on a set of premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest example of a modern classic that has been cared for by a non-smoker and kept garaged. Ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
